(1765, 'Alex Liu', 'alexinsurance1979@hotmail.com', 'insurance fraud', 'Dear Government and insurance company representatives, I am Alex Liu and currently contacted you from Hong Kong at this moment. There has been an incident on going within this country and I feel like my life is in danger living under the jurisdiction of the Hong Kong Government. With the utmost urgency I wanted to inform you about a sinister criminal activities related to the Triads members involved in stalking random innocent people in Hong Kong, and I’m also one of the victim. Since I’m a British citizen therefore I feel like I have the responsibility to inform you about this matter because I’m very concerned that the Triads gangster are specifically targeted random and isolated individuals in order to rob their life insurances and personal assets. They usually target foreigner or regular civilian like me because their plan is to choose the easiest target to commit a crime against them. The current Hong Kong is not really a safe haven to travel to especially for foreigner because since the Chinese government take over after 1997 the rule of law foundation here is really deteriorating at a rapid rate. Because of this reason the triads has exploit the situation to murder random people and getting away with their personal life insurance and assets without subject to prosecution. The triads have many connections with international criminal organizations, such as the mafia within the US, UK, Russia, Middle East and some Africa countries, they all belong to a same group of criminals and work towards a same goal which is to murder random individuals around the world to rob their life insurance as well as their personal assets, this is also their main source of revenue that the triads use to expand their criminal enterprise. The triads have many of their own members working within the insurance companies, so that it will be easier for them to establish fraudulent contract on the victim without their approval and signature. They also have some of their own members work as a lawyers, the triads are very experience on using their lawyers to make false document to rob the victims personal assets including their estate, bank saving and inheritance from the victim’s family member, usually once the victim died the triads will be able to claimed everything, and also a portion of the victim’s money will be used to fund their other criminal activities.\\nThe triads are trying to use slow acting poison to murder my brother and me, because I think they already set us as a target and trying to rob us. I believed that we are not the only target they are after; the triads already have many of their members stationed in other countries targeting isolated and wealthy families. They also inject some kind of tracking device in our body to track our movement; they wanted to be precise on knowing where we are going to shop our grocery next time, this will allow them to better prepare to poison our food and drinks. The tracking device also can generate large dose of radiation to kill the victim slowly and cause cancer, they also have plan to use this method to fraud the medical insurance using us as a baits. \\nI have tried to contact the Hong Kong Police and ICAC before about this incident but unfortunately the gangsters are using all kinds of methods trying to discredit me and prevent me to receive outside support. \\nThe triads are also planning to create an accident in our house with the shower and cooking gas to explode in order for them to claim money from the accidental death, home and fire insurance policy. Many of the victims were murder this way and the triads can circumvent any suspicion from insurance staff and police along with getting away with the accidental, fire and home coverage. In addition, the triads has been fumigate poisonous gasses into the victim’s house, which I believe they have tried this covert assassination method on me as well. The poisonous gas usually